  &lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click on the “Modify” link for the Capacity setting. Set your “Environment Type” to “Load balanced” and determine the maximum and minimum number of instances you want to run. I chose 0 for the min and 1 for the max since I only need to run one instance for when the job is running, and won’t need to run any instances when the job isn’t running.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
