  &lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Change the “Scale up increment” and “Scale down increment” to 0 since we won’t need to auto-scale based on any of the given parameters. We only need to scale based on the times we enter under the “Time-based Scaling” section.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
